ast.name: Insect Smasher
ast.comment: Insects are flying around in your phone. Smash them and they will go away, but they will come back faster and more annoying.  When there are five insects, the game is over. Version 1.1: 13 different insects in the same style; decreased delay to show effect of tapping from 0.1 to 0.01 second; improvements on increasing difficulty.
